Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.70,0:00:24.90,标题,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\c&H5F58AC&}「人鱼族的同居日常」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.92,0:01:31.92,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,brume0425仅分享于伊莉论坛/动画下载区(免空)请勿任意转载
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.92,0:01:33.45,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,紧急事态！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.00,0:01:37.26,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我们所保护的史莱姆  苏的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.43,0:01:39.66,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,被政府发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.12,0:01:42.59,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,但对方拥有国家权力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.59,0:01:43.99,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,该怎么对抗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.99,0:01:46.60,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling参谋  有什么解决方案吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.60,0:01:48.02,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,别突然把问题丢给我啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.53,0:01:50.89,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,感觉你们突然变成苏的同伴了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.89,0:01:56.14,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,因为  这孩子不会成为争夺Darling的对手嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.83,0:02:00.28,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我只服从主公的决定
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.46,0:02:03.73,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我是他种族交流法保安局的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.73,0:02:04.29,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.29,0:02:08.40,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,来留主先生  多谢平日的照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.40,0:02:09.54,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,失礼了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.66,0:02:16.05,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,大家呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.19,0:02:21.05,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,收留了这么多留学生寄宿  真是出色的宿主呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.43,0:02:24.00,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,苏的房间？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.00,0:02:27.61,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,什么啊  墨须小姐原来也有意外温柔的一面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.65,0:02:32.23,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,到这里应该就没问题了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.49,0:02:35.23,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,在风波平息前就先藏起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.42,0:02:38.74,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我说我说  我们丢下主人没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.91,0:02:41.27,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,糟糕！把那么重要的事给忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.27,0:02:44.24,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,没跟Darling在一起的话  我们也会被逮捕的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.62,0:02:46.50,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,快藏起来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.51,0:02:50.10,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,找到了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.10,0:02:51.42,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,没有  找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.42,0:02:52.59,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,到底去哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.59,0:02:53.90,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,去那边找找看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.90,0:02:54.88,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.14,0:02:56.30,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,追兵吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.30,0:02:57.73,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,来得异常的快
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.38,0:03:00.31,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,帕皮？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.89,0:03:05.50,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.50,0:03:09.39,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,因为苏想喝水  就把宝特瓶给…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.44,0:03:13.33,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,马上就干了  忍耐一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.05,0:03:14.90,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,这次又怎…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.62,0:03:22.78,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,等…你要干什么？苏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.97,0:03:28.29,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,是在舔取水分吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.68,0:03:31.29,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,等…等一下  苏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.22,0:03:36.29,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,想…想喝水的话我会帮你拿的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.70,0:03:40.55,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,快…快住手  苏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.06,0:03:45.55,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,好…好像  帕皮  好像…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.30,0:03:52.16,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,这…这个是！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.16,0:03:54.50,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,湿了的话  会被干掉！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.80,0:03:57.79,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,真是的  到底去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.79,0:04:01.12,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,难得墨须小姐准备苏的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.09,0:04:05.41,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,谁…谁来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.69,0:04:07.56,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,请来救救我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.56,0:04:08.66,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,谁来…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.50,0:04:20.76,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,软软的安全气囊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.38,0:04:24.06,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,你…你没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.06,0:04:25.99,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,要叫救护车来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.35,0:04:28.00,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,没事没事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.00,0:04:29.43,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,平常都会有的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.57,0:04:35.58,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,谢谢您在危急关头救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.64,0:04:38.26,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,请容我自我介绍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.26,0:04:40.11,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我叫作梅洛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.43,0:04:42.32,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,真的十分感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.32,0:04:43.58,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,你…你好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.58,0:04:45.50,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我叫来留主公人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.50,0:04:47.17,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那么我就到这
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.17,0:04:49.92,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我还在寻找他种族的女孩们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.92,0:04:54.33,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,莫非是拉米亚族  哈耳庇厄族  半人马族的女孩们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.22,0:04:56.83,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那样的话  我刚才看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.82,0:05:01.18,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,真头痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.60,0:05:04.34,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,没想到脱水的苏这么难处理
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.53,0:05:07.34,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,黑衣人也变多了  怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.11,0:05:11.85,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,既然这样只能趁他们不注意移动到别处了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.38,0:05:13.35,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.75,0:05:15.71,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,你那是什么表情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.71,0:05:18.32,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,还有其他能藏身的地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.32,0:05:21.16,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,因为珊卓雷雅屁股很大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.16,0:05:23.49,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,你的尾巴也不是很长吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.88,0:05:28.37,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,呀啊  弄坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.37,0:05:29.34,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,啰嗦！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.34,0:05:32.12,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我没想到那里有水龙头
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.12,0:05:36.37,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,湿成这样好厉害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.37,0:05:38.35,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,就像是失禁一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.96,0:05:44.63,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,喂  等…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.15,0:05:46.65,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,快住手  苏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.65,0:05:48.13,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,想喝水去水龙头那里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.94,0:05:51.03,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不能发出声音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.03,0:05:52.45,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,会被发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.84,0:05:55.49,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,加油  珊卓雷雅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.49,0:05:58.71,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,只要吸收完水分  苏就会安静下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.14,0:06:04.15,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,口水…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.78,0:06:15.16,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,珊卓雷雅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.14,0:06:22.17,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,怎…怎么了  从公园传来了好强的杀气
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.63,0:06:28.43,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,既然如此  就来持久战
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.72,0:06:30.43,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,奉陪到底了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.82,0:06:32.78,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,话说  去喝那边的水啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.69,0:06:40.77,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,你在做什么呢  米亚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.50,0:06:42.15,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.87,0:06:44.70,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,这…这是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.70,0:06:46.04,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,苏…袭…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.35,0:06:51.07,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,明明身上哪里都没湿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.33,0:06:56.33,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,糟糕！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.70,0:07:06.35,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,为什么知道我的弱点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.55,0:07:10.68,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Da…Darling  不要看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.19,0:07:22.27,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,咦！我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.32,0:07:30.07,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不愧是已经习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.35,0:07:38.82,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那么防水房间就完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.62,0:07:41.98,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.98,0:07:43.88,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那么辛苦究竟为了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.88,0:07:45.79,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,太好了  苏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.16,0:07:49.47,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,拜托您明天签好这里的文件
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.22,0:07:54.44,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,装修完成了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.44,0:07:55.80,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,墨须小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.80,0:07:59.98,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,求你不要只安排施工却完全不露面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.98,0:08:01.68,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,墨须小姐  墨须小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.68,0:08:05.11,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,谢谢你为了苏建造了房间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.11,0:08:06.34,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,听好了  大家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.34,0:08:09.44,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我可是要做各种工作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.70,0:08:11.23,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,又要帮留学生找寄宿家庭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.23,0:08:13.38,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,又要监视是否有人违反他种族交流法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.38,0:08:14.76,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,又要执行新的方案
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.76,0:08:16.45,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,但薪水却没涨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.45,0:08:17.20,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,再加上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.20,0:08:19.94,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,偷渡入境和新种他种族什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.94,0:08:23.21,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,说实话  干脆就不管了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.74,0:08:25.00,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,咦！？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.43,0:08:29.35,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,所以我对史莱姆的他种族什么的  看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.35,0:08:30.25,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,请多指教！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.25,0:08:31.71,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,这样可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.71,0:08:32.60,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,好随意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.60,0:08:34.14,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,嘛  太好了  苏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.18,0:08:38.25,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那为什么要帮苏建造房间呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.22,0:08:40.08,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.08,0:08:42.52,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,哦~那个房间是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.52,0:08:45.52,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,失礼了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.15,0:08:50.53,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,大家贵安！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.86,0:08:53.13,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,哎  为什么你会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.13,0:08:55.66,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,你擅自外出让我们很困扰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.66,0:08:57.53,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,你知道我们找你找得有多辛苦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.26,0:08:59.85,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.85,0:09:03.34,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,但是无论如何我都想看看城镇的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.34,0:09:07.44,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,然后偶然  被寄宿家庭的人救了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.44,0:09:09.25,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,简直就是命运
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.82,0:09:11.20,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,寄宿家庭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.20,0:09:13.18,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,是说要寄宿到我家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.18,0:09:13.76,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,咦！？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.02,0:09:15.80,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那Darling君
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.80,0:09:18.04,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,再正式介绍一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.04,0:09:19.22,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,这孩子是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.62,0:09:26.83,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我是人鱼族的美洛努·罗雷莱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.83,0:09:30.35,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,今天开始寄宿在您家中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.84,0:09:33.62,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,请您多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.08,0:09:35.53,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,老爷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.42,0:09:38.75,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\3c&H0000FF&}魔物娘！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.24,0:09:44.50,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\3c&H0000FF&}魔物娘！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.37,0:09:51.58,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,这样可以吗？梅洛小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.99,0:09:54.55,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,请叫我美洛  老爷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.00,0:09:56.35,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那么要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.74,0:09:58.94,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,嗯  一起去吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.67,0:10:02.31,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.50,0:10:05.20,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,你在做什么  跟她卿卿我我的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.20,0:10:07.19,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,等  米亚  你在干…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.13,0:10:15.90,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,您没事吧  老爷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.90,0:10:18.78,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,等等  Darling要由我来担心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.73,0:10:27.96,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,真是的  你在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.41,0:10:31.44,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我抱着她只是带她去去二楼看看而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.44,0:10:33.35,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,可…可是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.82,0:10:37.47,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,墨须小姐说待会会把新轮椅拿来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.00,0:10:40.41,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,在那之前我来抱她走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.41,0:10:41.97,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Da…Darling！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.72,0:10:44.50,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,米亚  你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.86,0:10:46.92,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,都是寄宿的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.92,0:10:47.98,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.38,0:10:51.34,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,争夺Darling的对手又增加了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.34,0:10:53.48,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,怎么可能还那么悠闲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.68,0:10:56.79,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,到目前为止因为珊卓雷雅也没有越过界线
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.79,0:10:57.85,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,而帕皮只是个小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.85,0:10:59.58,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,苏的话  在问题外！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.58,0:11:02.79,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我才能站在候补新娘第一这个位置
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.79,0:11:05.24,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,你是这么看我们的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.33,0:11:09.54,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,再说她也不一定有那种想法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.54,0:11:11.41,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,好棒的宅邸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.86,0:11:15.60,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,话说回来  老爷你有恋人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.60,0:11:17.05,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,瞄上了！！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.28,0:11:18.80,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,你…你突然问什…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.70,0:11:23.93,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Da…Darling
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.54,0:11:25.48,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不  这是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.91,0:11:28.45,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,事发突然不小心…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.30,0:11:34.49,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling  真色
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.49,0:11:35.79,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,你是故意的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.79,0:11:36.98,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不…不是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.98,0:11:40.85,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不  人鱼的身体为了防止干燥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.85,0:11:42.85,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,上面布满了黏液
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.85,0:11:46.70,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,所以衣服会滑落也是常有的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.25,0:11:48.76,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.76,0:11:51.63,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,如果是老爷的话  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.37,0:11:53.73,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,是没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.49,0:11:56.84,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,已经开始攻略了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.61,0:11:59.04,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,可恶…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.04,0:12:01.70,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,黏黏滑滑的人有苏就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.70,0:12:03.23,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,黏液啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.23,0:12:05.85,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,所以苏才袭击了她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.06,0:12:09.06,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,苏  和姐姐去那边玩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.62,0:12:11.18,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,这里是客房
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.18,0:12:12.62,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那么接下来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.62,0:12:13.98,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.39,0:12:15.22,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,讨厌~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.22,0:12:17.62,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不要这么盯着我看嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.62,0:12:20.74,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我跟苏一起玩后全身就湿湿黏黏了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.13,0:12:23.07,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,以眼还眼  以牙还牙！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.07,0:12:24.91,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,以湿滑还湿滑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.45,0:12:28.49,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我不会把Darling让给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.06,0:12:31.42,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那样的话…去洗个澡就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.42,0:12:32.50,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,热水已经放好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.70,0:12:36.19,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,可恶的Darling！居然这么体贴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.19,0:12:37.23,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我最喜欢你这点了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.23,0:12:39.48,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,但是这样下去会如那家伙所愿了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.74,0:12:42.51,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,米亚  你有点意识过剩了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.74,0:12:43.94,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,你在说什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.94,0:12:46.41,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,她突然来寄宿  还对Darling抛媚眼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.41,0:12:48.01,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,背里肯定有什么阴谋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.41,0:12:51.40,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,无论如何也不能让Darling被她抢走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.40,0:12:55.52,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,既然如此  就用空调让房间变冷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.44,0:12:59.80,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,为身为人鱼…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.85,0:13:00.91,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,而穿泳衣…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.15,0:13:05.03,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,感~到~后~悔~吧~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.27,0:13:07.55,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,难道不是你在后悔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.82,0:13:10.43,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,怎感觉有点冷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.43,0:13:12.58,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,今天有这么冷吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.58,0:13:13.54,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,梅洛你不要紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.28,0:13:17.64,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,是  人鱼对低温有抗性
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.64,0:13:18.84,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,只是小事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.24,0:13:20.84,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,米亚  振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.84,0:13:22.30,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,睡着会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.30,0:13:23.30,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,是不是在冬眠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.65,0:13:25.39,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,什么啊  原来开了空调了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.95,0:13:30.05,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,哇！设定的温度好高
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.46,0:13:31.63,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,咦？不会动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.61,0:13:33.82,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,是没电了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.00,0:13:35.06,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.28,0:13:36.07,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.06,0:13:41.44,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,好暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.06,0:13:46.53,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,既然如此我们三人合力保护Darling
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.53,0:13:48.36,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,你想把我们也牵扯进去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.76,0:13:50.90,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我们的关系写作对手  读作同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.90,0:13:52.62,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,帕皮也会来帮我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.98,0:13:55.04,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,呐  来玩游戏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.37,0:13:56.37,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,瞬间脱离
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.91,0:13:57.93,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,帕皮小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.93,0:14:01.13,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,老爷有恋爱的对象了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.15,0:14:03.95,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我也不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.05,0:14:08.35,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,看来你很担心主公的男女关系
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.77,0:14:11.15,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,你对这类话题很感兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.15,0:14:13.57,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,是  虽然有点害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.57,0:14:17.00,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,因为人鱼公主的童话在人鱼之间很受欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.00,0:14:18.54,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,人鱼公主是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.54,0:14:21.53,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,是一个爱上人类王子的人鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.66,0:14:24.25,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,用她的歌声为代价
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.25,0:14:25.94,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,变成了人类
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.94,0:14:26.97,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,结果
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.97,0:14:31.71,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,未能实现恋情而成泡沫消失的悲伤爱情故事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.47,0:14:35.55,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,人鱼们都对Love的罗曼史没有抵抗力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.55,0:14:40.85,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我也经常会去看演绎悲伤爱情的歌剧或音乐剧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.58,0:14:43.17,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,歌剧或音乐剧…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.82,0:14:45.86,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,无论是你说话方式或礼仪举止
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.86,0:14:49.18,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,特别是身上散发的氛围  和一般人差太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.70,0:14:52.18,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,况且那个随意的墨须小姐居然对你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.18,0:14:54.03,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,使用了敬语
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.10,0:14:57.18,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,实在很让人在意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.22,0:14:59.57,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不愧是珊卓雷雅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.57,0:15:01.19,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,总感觉很可靠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.70,0:15:06.10,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,珊卓雷雅小姐是老爷的恋人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.10,0:15:06.69,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,什！？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.18,0:15:10.25,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,恋恋恋…恋人什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.25,0:15:12.20,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我只是侍奉主公之人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.86,0:15:14.85,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,和传闻中的一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.38,0:15:19.94,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我听说半人马族是很有荣耀感的一族
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.94,0:15:21.06,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.06,0:15:23.71,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我能从你身上感受到更高贵的信念
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.10,0:15:25.08,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.08,0:15:27.82,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,就像是宣誓对主公绝对的忠诚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.82,0:15:29.47,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,中世纪的骑士一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.50,0:15:32.92,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,怎么回事  这家伙释放出的气场…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.92,0:15:36.47,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,简直就像是在一国之主面前一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.12,0:15:42.84,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,从未奢求过能遇见像你这样有着高贵荣誉感的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.46,0:15:46.11,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,感谢这如同奇迹般的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.54,0:15:48.04,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,珊卓雷雅大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.04,0:15:49.36,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,啊…是！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.58,0:15:52.36,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,期待你今后还能尽己所能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.64,0:15:54.30,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,是  就算粉身碎骨…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.30,0:15:56.24,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,快回来  中世纪的骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.24,0:15:57.86,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,呃…我到底怎么…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.22,0:16:00.63,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,真是的  总之
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.63,0:16:03.06,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我绝对不会把Darling让给你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.06,0:16:03.62,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,你明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.52,0:16:07.85,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我并没有那个意图
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.29,0:16:13.01,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,绝对  不会发生那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.69,0:16:16.63,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,好热  我找到电池了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.80,0:16:18.78,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,梅洛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.78,0:16:19.97,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.97,0:16:24.22,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,人鱼只要让鳃保持湿润  也能在陆地上呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.22,0:16:26.83,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,但暖气让空气变干燥了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.83,0:16:28.52,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那我带你回房间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.52,0:16:30.64,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,非常感谢  老爷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.64,0:16:32.81,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,米亚  拜托你换电池了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.09,0:16:38.28,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,她绝对在策划些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.06,0:16:41.29,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,米亚  你适可而止
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.46,0:16:46.29,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,都是你弄坏了轮椅  主公才会一直照顾她
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.77,0:16:50.03,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,憧憬童话的人又不只她一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.03,0:16:50.80,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.27,0:16:55.86,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,童话中的公主一定会被王子所救
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.86,0:17:00.43,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,之后公主和王子会一直幸福地生活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.08,0:17:04.94,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,所以我的梦想就是被王子公主抱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.60,0:17:08.08,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我也能被王子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.77,0:17:10.57,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.78,0:17:14.03,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那个人鱼却享受着Darling的公主抱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.36,0:17:17.01,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,这从物理上来说不太可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.31,0:17:21.77,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那家伙  用泳衣来诱惑Darling
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.77,0:17:24.29,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那你也穿上泳衣不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.81,0:17:31.26,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,老爷真的没有恋人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.26,0:17:33.14,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,没…没有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.14,0:17:35.48,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,你为什么那么在意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.48,0:17:36.87,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.22,0:17:39.51,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.86,0:17:47.18,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,这个泳池果然好大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.18,0:17:49.90,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我想来游泳  可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.90,0:17:50.98,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,嗯  请
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.29,0:17:52.48,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,呐~Darling
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.78,0:17:54.26,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,一起来游泳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.26,0:17:55.49,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不…不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.06,0:17:57.90,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,这样就站到同一起跑点上了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.90,0:18:00.43,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不如说露出度是我赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.43,0:18:02.98,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,绝对不会让你为所欲为了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.20,0:18:04.73,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.10,0:18:07.75,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,你在干什么  快点进来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.06,0:18:10.38,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不…不是…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.38,0:18:12.34,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不必那么介意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.34,0:18:13.75,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那…那就
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.70,0:18:21.28,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,被你给诱惑了该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.28,0:18:24.01,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,还不是你借我的泳衣太小了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.54,0:18:27.87,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那条特大号的沙滩巾在哪里找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.87,0:18:30.77,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,这是…那个…床单
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.77,0:18:32.82,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,你在干什么？帕皮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.82,0:18:34.53,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,苏  不知道去哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.89,0:18:36.46,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,她在不在这里面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.46,0:18:38.03,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,怎么可能在！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.29,0:18:43.73,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,失…失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.23,0:18:47.04,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,她们到底是来做什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.90,0:18:48.88,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.88,0:18:50.79,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,这样叛徒就…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.23,0:18:55.80,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.51,0:18:58.80,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那家伙露出本性了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.18,0:19:00.55,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,别对Darling出手！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.44,0:19:03.05,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,好深
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.89,0:19:05.06,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.45,0:19:07.14,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Da…Darling
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.30,0:19:11.41,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.41,0:19:13.26,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,体温在下降
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.26,0:19:14.98,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,身体要动不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.84,0:19:18.22,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,别说要救Darling了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.22,0:19:18.99,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我自己都…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.57,0:19:23.26,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Da…Darling
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.57,0:19:30.50,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,米亚！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.14,0:19:35.42,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.10,0:19:48.87,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,谢谢  Darling
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.87,0:19:49.75,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.75,0:19:51.86,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不要紧吧  米亚小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.54,0:19:53.94,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,啊  怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.94,0:19:55.39,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,身体居然这么冰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.39,0:19:58.44,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,让我用我的体温给你温暖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.44,0:19:59.29,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,咦！？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.29,0:20:01.10,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,梅洛小姐  冷静一点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.10,0:20:04.88,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,米亚  浴池水还热的可以直接进去泡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.16,0:20:06.94,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,嗯嗯…苏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.30,0:20:09.14,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,快住手  苏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.14,0:20:10.95,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,暖气把她也烘干了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.95,0:20:12.71,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,看来好像在寻找水呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.50,0:20:16.21,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,刚才也是  突然朝我飞过来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.52,0:20:19.43,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,是…是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.14,0:20:22.50,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,先去泡澡  米亚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.90,0:20:25.09,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我也一起  可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.91,0:20:30.63,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,真暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.63,0:20:34.54,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,这就是这个国家所说的坦诚相见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.54,0:20:35.60,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,梅洛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.18,0:20:37.08,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.48,0:20:40.86,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,对不起  对你做了很多失礼的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.26,0:20:42.62,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.62,0:20:43.86,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,你没发现吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.10,0:20:48.06,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,因为梅洛很自然的和Darling那么要好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.06,0:20:49.86,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,让我有点吃醋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.26,0:20:51.37,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.87,0:20:52.59,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.64,0:20:58.20,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling的新娘宝座我是不会让给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.54,0:20:59.55,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,绝对不会！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.78,0:21:00.98,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,新娘？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.98,0:21:03.78,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不  我并没有那样的打算
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.01,0:21:06.76,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我不是说过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.76,0:21:09.64,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我很憧憬人鱼公主那种罗曼史…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.02,0:21:11.09,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,既然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.09,0:21:12.07,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.07,0:21:13.84,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我非常憧憬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.84,0:21:17.38,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,像人鱼公主那样的…悲恋！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.93,0:21:20.95,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我不会妨碍米亚小姐的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.95,0:21:24.32,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不对  不如说我衷心祝福你能和老爷结合
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.32,0:21:26.54,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我想要谈一场悲恋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.54,0:21:30.17,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,想要向老爷献上绝不会有回报的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.17,0:21:34.00,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,所…所以我会作为情人为大家应援的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.00,0:21:39.02,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不过希望你们能容忍一下老爷的出轨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.63,0:21:43.76,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling是我一个人的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.00,0:21:43.76,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,梅洛  让人不能大意的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.31,0:21:48.76,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,已经变得那么要好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.72,0:23:22.60,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\c&HA0CCF9&\3c&H000000&}我连蜕皮都蜕不好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.81,0:23:27.23,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\c&HA0CCF9&\3c&H000000&}难得Darling肯正视我们  认真考虑结婚的事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.23,0:23:28.98,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\c&HA0CCF9&\3c&H000000&}我却无法做出回应
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.98,0:23:30.28,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\c&HA0CCF9&\3c&H000000&}太不像样了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.26,0:23:34.85,标题,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\pos(648,466)\c&HCB78A5&}「蜕皮与产卵的日常」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.28,0:23:32.10,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\c&HA0CCF9&\3c&H000000&}主人  主人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.10,0:23:34.62,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\c&HA0CCF9&\3c&H000000&}帕皮好像要产卵了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.40,0:00:05.82,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,Monster Monster
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.83,0:00:09.47,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,MonMonMonMon Monster
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.48,0:00:12.99,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,Monster Monster
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.00,0:00:18.81,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,MonMonMonMon Monster's life
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.41,0:00:28.11,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,其一  不要在意他人的目光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.11,0:00:30.67,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,要大胆以及慎重地选择目标
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.69,0:00:33.21,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,其二  日常问候要适度
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.31,0:00:36.69,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,当做好心理准备的话  就上阵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.70,0:00:40.45,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,其三  发现机会就要迅速瞄准
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.54,0:00:42.08,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,开火开火开火开火！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.09,0:00:44.57,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,其四  不需要去顾虑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.59,0:00:47.45,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,最后确实给目标的心致命一击而已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.46,0:00:52.16,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,只要有爱的话  就算只有一分也足够
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.17,0:00:58.38,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,比那个更重要的是  遵循欲望的指引
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.39,0:01:01.39,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,冲吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.89,0:01:04.00,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,嘿！亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.05,0:01:06.81,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,因为有你在所以才会是最强的是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.82,0:01:09.44,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,如果能一直在一起那就是最棒的不是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.45,0:01:11.97,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,无论前方会遇到什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.98,0:01:14.77,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,只要和你就 All OK！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.78,0:01:17.34,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,如今以无庸置疑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.34,0:01:20.08,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,这肯定就是宇宙第一的爱对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.09,0:01:24.46,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,等不及你的答案  我已经
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.56,0:01:29.33,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,最高速坠入爱河！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,OP-JP,brume0425,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.40,0:00:05.82,OP-JP,brume0425,0,0,0,,モンスター  モンスター
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.83,0:00:09.47,OP-JP,brume0425,0,0,0,,モンモンモンモン  モンスター
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.48,0:00:12.99,OP-JP,brume0425,0,0,0,,モンスター  モンスター
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.00,0:00:18.81,OP-JP,brume0425,0,0,0,,モンモンモンモン  モンスターズライフ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.41,0:00:28.11,OP-JP,brume0425,0,0,0,,一つ、人目ばっかり気にしてないで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.11,0:00:30.67,OP-JP,brume0425,0,0,0,,大胆に、かつ慎重にターゲットを決める
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.69,0:00:33.21,OP-JP,brume0425,0,0,0,,二つ、あいさつはほどほどに
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.31,0:00:36.69,OP-JP,brume0425,0,0,0,,ココロの準備が済んだら、いざ尋常に！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.70,0:00:40.45,OP-JP,brume0425,0,0,0,,三つ、見つけた隙は即座に狙い定め
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.54,0:00:42.08,OP-JP,brume0425,0,0,0,,撃つべし撃つべし撃つべし撃つべし！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.09,0:00:44.57,OP-JP,brume0425,0,0,0,,四つ、遠慮は必要ないさ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.59,0:00:47.45,OP-JP,brume0425,0,0,0,,あとは確実にハートを仕留めるだけで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.46,0:00:52.16,OP-JP,brume0425,0,0,0,,愛だったら、ほんのちょっとでいい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.17,0:00:58.38,OP-JP,brume0425,0,0,0,,それより何より、欲望のおもむくまま、
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.39,0:01:01.39,OP-JP,brume0425,0,0,0,,さぁ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.89,0:01:04.00,OP-JP,brume0425,0,0,0,,ねぇだぁりん
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.05,0:01:06.81,OP-JP,brume0425,0,0,0,,キミがいるから最強じゃない？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.82,0:01:09.44,OP-JP,brume0425,0,0,0,,ずっと一緒なら最高じゃない？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.45,0:01:11.97,OP-JP,brume0425,0,0,0,,この先何があったって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.98,0:01:14.77,OP-JP,brume0425,0,0,0,,キミとなら All OK！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.78,0:01:17.34,OP-JP,brume0425,0,0,0,,もはやこれは紛れもない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.35,0:01:20.08,OP-JP,brume0425,0,0,0,,宇宙で一番のLOVEなんじゃない？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.09,0:01:24.46,OP-JP,brume0425,0,0,0,,答え待ちきれないんだよ、もう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.56,0:01:29.33,OP-JP,brume0425,0,0,0,,最高速 Fall in Love！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,ED-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.86,0:22:05.22,ED-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,OY! OY! OY! Hey Sumisu!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.23,0:22:09.26,ED-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,OY! OY! OY! Hey Sumisu!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.27,0:22:11.43,ED-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,点燃手中拥有的权力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.44,0:22:13.32,ED-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,毫无疑问的个人主义
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.77,0:22:15.85,ED-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,还记得吗随时光流逝的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.85,0:22:17.88,ED-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,真实如同海市蜃楼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.15,0:22:20.71,ED-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,这不是逃跑是脚停不下来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.71,0:22:22.55,ED-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,那才是我的美学
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.60,0:22:25.20,ED-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,规律对我自身来说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.20,0:22:26.88,ED-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,毫无意义
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.89,0:22:31.34,ED-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,徒劳无功(徒劳无功) 功过事迹(功过事迹)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.34,0:22:35.53,ED-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,扭扭腰(扭扭腰) 发出声响
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.38,0:22:38.42,ED-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,HEY！！我们代表正义
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.70,0:22:40.26,ED-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,HEY！！我们不容置疑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.42,0:22:43.93,ED-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,如果真实是这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.26,0:22:47.54,ED-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,HEY！！场面大话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.58,0:22:49.19,ED-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,HEY！！我不会说
